%HRTitleEvent Squeeze
%bridge-classroom-stable: true















[showcards N:S5,HJ,CK,C7 E:SJ,ST,CQ,CT S:SK,CA,C8,C4 W:HQ,CJ,C9,C5]

It is now time to pressure West. 

Play dummy's \S5 to your \SK.

West MUST keep his \HQ so he releases his \C5.

And you win the last three tricks with \CK, \CA, \C8.

This is called a Double Squeeze.}
[Play "W"]HK

[Event "Baker Bridge - Squeeze Plays"]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "2"]
[Dealer "N"]
[Vulnerable "NS"]
[Deal "N:AK74.AK5.KQT.AK2 QJT83.JT72.63.T6 952.6.AJ974.Q843 6.Q9843.852.J975"]
[Declarer "N"]
[Contract "7NT"]
[Result ""]
[Auction "N"]
2C pass 3D pass 4NT pass 5D pass 7NT pass pass pass
[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 2, chOption: N, chBasis: S, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:0, nBasis: 2, nRot: 2, useStandardVul: true"]
[BoardVersionToken "7202b0029d1efd40d9bb92459da730ad13e416caa3e9719e87d1b6d179f59339"]
