[Auction "E"]
1H 1S 2C pass 3H pass 4H pass 4NT pass 5D pass 6H pass pass pass
[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 4, chOption: E, chBasis: S, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:1, nBasis: 2, nRot: 3, useStandardVul: true"]
[BoardVersionToken "835eda48a403a4bd440de8ddd439a077be66e8a880b1b6536c48c7a38a15e1c1"]
[Category "Declarer Play"]
